🎯 10 Most Asked Computer Network Interview Questions (FINAL MASTER SET)
1️⃣ What is OSI model?

7-layer network architecture.

2️⃣ What is TCP/IP?

Practical 4-layer model.

3️⃣ What is DNS?

Name to IP mapping system.

4️⃣ What is TCP?

Reliable connection-oriented protocol.

5️⃣ What is UDP?

Fast connectionless protocol.

6️⃣ What is HTTP vs HTTPS?

HTTP = plain, HTTPS = secure.

7️⃣ What is NAT?

Private to public IP mapping.

8️⃣ What is routing?

Path selection for packets.

9️⃣ What is subnetting?

Dividing network into smaller parts.

🔟 What is firewall?

Network traffic control system.

